comments: I got her and her mom

Her class was great. Anthea is very sharp intellectually and also very nice. If you pay attention and keep up with the class you will learn a lot. You will enjoy it too. She helped me be a better critical thinker which I now see is very important in writing.

This class is as bland as oatmeal and so is she. No passion, quiet. Nice person. MANDATORY attendance. Leave 10 minutes earlier? She\'ll make sure she deducts that for points. Useless class- didn\'t learn a thing. I want a refund!
